result.longName: Nanjing Inform Storage Equipment (Group) Co., Ltd.

assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Nanjing Inform Storage Equipment (Group) Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, researches and develops, manufactures, sells, and installs shelf and storage equipment in China. The company offers racking solutions, including automated storage and retrieval systems; multi-tier mezzanine racks; longspan, carton flow, radio shuttle, drive-in, push back, live in, cantilever, and electric mobile racking systems; and automation equipment and sets, as well as boltless shelving and selective pallet racking systems. It also provides logistic equipment, such as plastic column guards, foldable mesh containers, steel pallets, and wire mesh panels; storage systems, including warehouse monitor and control software, shuttle systems for pallet comprising shuttle carrier, shuttle and stacker crane, shuttle and forklift, four-way shuttle, and 360°AGV systems; and shuttle systems for bins, such as in shuttle car picking, light duty stack crane, and carousel racking systems, as well as storage operation services. In addition, the company offers metal forming products, mechanical parking equipment, steel structures, warehouse management software, logistics equipment control software, and basic equipment. Further, it provides technical services and development, supply chain management and related supporting services, business information municipal planning and consultation, and warehousing services. Additionally, the company is involved in the design, sale, and installation of handling equipment; design, manufacture, installation, and sale of hardware products; and leasing of equipment. The company was formerly known as Nanjing Inform Storage Equipment Co., Ltd. and changed its name to Nanjing Inform Storage Equipment (Group) Co., Ltd. in November 2016. Nanjing Inform Storage Equipment (Group) Co., Ltd. was founded in 2002 and is based in Nanjing, China.
